<h1 class="mb-4">
    <i class="bi bi-plus-slash-minus me-2"></i> Custom Formula Engagement Rate
</h1>

<% if (message) { %>
    <div class="alert alert-<%= success ? 'success' : 'danger' %> alert-dismissible fade show">
        <i class="bi bi-<%= success ? 'check-circle' : 'exclamation-triangle' %> me-2"></i>
        <%= decodeURIComponent(message) %>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
    </div>
<% } %>

<div class="alert alert-info">
    <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-2"></i>
    <strong>Engagement Rate Formula:</strong> Gunakan variabel seperti like, comment, view, dll.
    <br>
    <strong>Target:</strong> Diisi manual di halaman analytics untuk setiap report.
    <br>
    <strong>Contoh Formula:</strong> (like + comment + share + save) / view * 100
</div>

<form method="POST" action="/reports/save-formula">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h5><i class="bi bi-bar-chart-line me-2"></i> Engagement Rate Formula</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <textarea name="engagement_formula" class="form-control" rows="6" 
                              placeholder="Contoh: (like + comment + share + save) / view * 100"
                              required><%= currentFormula?.engagement_formula || '' %></textarea>
                    <small class="text-muted">
                        <strong>Variabel yang tersedia:</strong><br>
                        like, comment, view, share, save, follower
                    </small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-4">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
            <i class="bi bi-save me-2"></i> Simpan Formula
        </button>
        <a href="/reports/analytics" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
            <i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-2"></i> Kembali ke Analytics
        </a>
    </div>
</form>

<div class="mt-4">
    <div class="card border-warning">
        <div class="card-header bg-warning text-dark">
            <h6><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i> Tips Penggunaan</h6>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <ul class="mb-0">
                <li>Formula mendukung operasi matematika: +, -, *, /, (), Math.min(), Math.max()</li>
                <li>Pastikan formula valid dan tidak menyebabkan error</li>
                <li>Formula akan diterapkan ke semua data yang ada</li>
                <li>Setiap kali menyimpan, formula lama akan dinonaktifkan</li>
                <li><strong>Target diatur manual per report di halaman analytics</strong></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
